g src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/13/120224_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F13%2F120224_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=09d1dbf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一般香港人入新界就見慣乳牛<br />\n不過入得天水圍咁大件事緊係唔可以騎埋依D一般貨色<br />\n新界佬有名你叫牛屎佬， 執慣牛屎架㗎嘛。比D牛屎佬見到你隻牛一時慣咗手勢一下揸落你隻牛到， 係咁揸係咁揸，啲奶就噴曬出嚟，幾撚失威<br />\n嗱，巴打。睇你條友都係一支公入新界，唔好話唔醒啲好嘢畀你<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/13/125203_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F13%2F125203_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e7aef426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依隻非洲安哥拉牛， 啫啫啫！你睇下佢隻角！又大又長簡直係男人雄風最佳象徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都知香港依家治安幾差，入天水圍長途跋涉，遇到II隻牛都可以頂走佢地<br />\n居家旅行，鋤強扶弱，止咳化痰必備<br />\n不過你想騎最好三五七日前book定先，搶手貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/13/124334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F13%2F124334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=475b4868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依隻蘇格蘭高地牛，mk仔至愛，溝女一流<br />\n你幻想下，騎住佢入到天水圍D mk妹牛咁眼望住你，跟著你一句：「妹妹仔，想唔想騎下牛牛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，即刻閪水長流啦。跟著都唔洗我教啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS:你食唔到女唔好出返黎九龍"},{"pid":"2f93be497a45fdd9af5db4a2702d097051adf4bd","tid":153361,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd965c2cf6807a358a948bae48b68aaf8364885","tid":153361,"uid":72816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"帶回鄉證，八達通，地圖<br />\n<br />\n記住唔好講錯野，會無命返嚟"},{"pid":"b69590df1bfa1810011a28e34b36e137fadf2bc8","tid":153361,"uid":28789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"記得帶返個營去訓啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665b556a4ae7388a6af8f7df8fbfc27f0b9dfbcc","tid":153361,"uid":1498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:55:27.000Z","msg":"小心比d蠻族用弓箭射你"}]}